Abamatekisi bakhala ngokuthi lezi zimoto ezithutha abantu kazinayo imvume futhi zilayisha noma yikuphi ngisho emarenke. Imenenja yehhovisi leSantaco KwaZulu Natal, uMnuz Sifiso Shangase, ithe abemboni yamatekisi yaseMgungundlovu, babhalela umasipala incwadi ngezikhalazo zabo ngalezi zimoto kodwa awuzange uphendule. “Sifuna ukuba basinake, basiphendule ngezikhalazo zethu njengoba senza kanje. Sivale idolobha nemigwaqo engenela kulo,” kuchaza uShangase. Udaba oluphelele ephephandabeni lakho kusasa.